{
  "stem": "833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, therefore, we had to also learn a different way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were the ones also who taught the different way, my brother and I and our friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, it was during the depression that I started-- the depression started in '29.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was at that time that I got my first opera engagement in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that was the time when radicalism became on every side [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a way of life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We became radical socialists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They became radical fascists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it is not known today that the socialists were still in the plurality all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they didn't have the support of the big business, the big industries, the big money sources that still were available.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The fascists got the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We got the voices.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So in Germany, we realized immediately that Hitler never got more than-- less than a third of the votes, while the socialists and the Communists got twice as many.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But the leadership was very stupid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They never would get together in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, in the fall of 1930-- in November of 1932, when I was in Dusseldorf-- a different job already-- it looked as if the people would rise up to the fascists' rankings.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, anyone with any senses would have listened at that time to Hitler's speeches, as I did--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I attended some of his meetings, some of his rallies in order to know, to learn what's happening because learning is a profession for me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he lost-- there were two elections in this year, one in March, one in November, '32.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he lost in November more than two million votes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Two million votes in America is nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
